@startuml
title Safehome Security Function State Machine

state "PowerOnCheck" as POC
state "StartupProblem" as SP
state "ReadyToUse" as RTU
state "Monitoring" as M
state "Normal" as N

POC --> RTU : everything working
POC --> SP : problem detected

SP --> POC : problem resolved
SP --> N : system stops

RTU --> POC : user resets
RTU --> M : user activates
RTU --> N : user turns off

M --> M : false alarm or time ends
M --> N : user enters password

@enduml
